            <title>[FELIX-4934] Only log failures for consistently failing bundles</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-4934</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Fileinstall logs failures at WARN even if the failure is an early attempt for which the dependency might already exist in the scan directories.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However, it&apos;s beneficial to get failure logs for the legitimate cases were dependencies are really missing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
